title: Pumpkin pie with streusel topping
ingredients: ['425g pumpkin puree', '1 (397g) tin sweetened condensed milk', '2 egg yolks', '1 teaspoon ground cinnamon', '1/2 teaspoon ground ginger', '1/2 teaspoon ground nutmeg', '1/2 teaspoon salt', '2 egg whites', '1 (23cm) unbaked sweet pastry case', '2 tablespoons plain flour', '4 tablespoons dark brown soft sugar', '1 teaspoon ground cinnamon', '30g unsalted butter, chilled', '110g walnuts, chopped']
